{"tid":2120919,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國駐英大使：倘英國選擇與中國脫鉤　就是與未來脫鉤","createTime":"2020-07-23T03:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T04:09:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c52c97a7aac757f83b93e4f32e61adc10e2983e8","tid":2120919,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539409-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539409-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgLXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=fbb4ccab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539409-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=90d3d166\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539409-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國駐英國大使劉曉明形容，如果英國選擇與中國「脫鉤」，就是與機遇脫鉤、與增長脫鉤、與未來脫鉤。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明在中國駐英大使館舉行的一個網上座談會表示，在「後脫歐時代」和「後疫情時代」，英國要打造「全球化英國」，離不開中國。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，英方近期犯了嚴重違反國際關係基本準則、對華認知與戰略定位出現嚴重錯誤的兩大錯誤，導致中英兩國關係急轉直下，出現一系列令人擔憂的困難和挫折。他又說，即使在當前中英關係面臨困難的情況下，英國政府也不得不承認，要與中國保持建設性關係，英國社會主流特別是工商界仍希望深化對華合作。"},{"pid":"2414587936b5b80c62da44c0f0cd6405ebb72447","tid":2120919,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"未來都可以係仆街冚家鏟嘅"},{"pid":"4e031d6b3a9310f76ebe06246ed91131cd1bf1be","tid":2120919,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"低能"},{"pid":"04576e48b18115dadda173c072c894b1353a9fa4","tid":2120919,"uid":43663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"與未來既大逃殺脫勾係好事"},{"pid":"af2e8494b4970fe216b77cbe8168afef3f3e56e1","tid":2120919,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"如果中國選擇與英國「脫鉤」，就是與機遇脫鉤、與增長脫鉤、與未來脫鉤。<br />\n<br />\n在「後脫歐時代」和「後疫情時代」，中國要打造「全球化中國」，離不開英國。<br />\n<br />\n中方近期犯了嚴重違反國際關係基本準則、對英認知與戰略定位出現嚴重錯誤的兩大錯誤，導致英中兩國關係急轉直下，出現一系列令人擔憂的困難和挫折。即使在當前英中關係面臨困難的情況下，中國政府也不得不承認，要與英國保持建設性關係，中國社會主流特別是工商界仍希望深化對華合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773f8e9026b0828a467f1afbd29ba51fff07d680","tid":2120919,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"乜中国有未來架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出年都唔知過唔過到"},{"pid":"8421ce5d873c6cbffeb55490345a36c0f14112d1","tid":2120919,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2414587936b5b80c62da44c0f0cd6405ebb72447","tid":2120919,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"未來都可以係仆街冚家鏟嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"人地指英國冇未來<br />\n即係話英國會滅國啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f1e1c3884164e02898380a1cdd79b1d5af6d1d","tid":2120919,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"未來還有中華人民共和國嗎？"},{"pid":"3c56c6fcb91bc75722369b4845f41ff3c8ecc381","tid":2120919,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"與集中營脫勾"},{"pid":"cf8fc3199db86e84bfb5210b60412dbead3a201c","tid":2120919,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XOilBE-d3yY/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FXOilBE-d3yY%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=8467d21d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3e9251a6d29c7d65b0a9a06b4266a69ee8534db","tid":2120919,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n記得買多啲其他國家嘅貨<br />\n中國製盡量唔買最好一蚊都唔落佢袋<br /